              <li>• Name</li>
              <li>• Email Address</li>
              <li>• Phone Number</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">2.2 Usage and Analytics Data</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Data about how you interact with our website (e.g., pages viewed, click patterns, time spent)</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">2.3 Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Devices, IP addresses, browser types, and other technical information collected via cookies and similar technologies.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">2.4 Collection Methods</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Directly from users when they fill out forms, create accounts, or contact us.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

