          <li>• Managing user accounts and authentication</li>
          <li>• Processing payments</li>
          <li>• Sending you updates and customer support communications</li>
          <li>• Analyzing site usage to improve our services</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">3.1 Legal Basis</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
