        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Your Privacy Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Depending on your jurisdiction, you have the following rights:</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Right to Access</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Request a copy of your personal data we hold</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Right to Correction</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Request correction or update of your data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Right to Deletion</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Request that we delete your personal data</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">How to Exercise Your Rights</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Send an email to <a href="mailto:hello@afida.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@afida.com</a>. You can also opt-out of cookies through your browser settings.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 6 -->
      <section id="security" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your data, including encryption, access controls, and secure storage.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">In the unlikely event of a data breach, we will notify affected individuals and authorities as required by law.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 7 -->
      <section id="international" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. International Data Transfers</h2>
